		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />My top-loading NES on my 13" Sony CRT looks like complete crap.  Then again, I shouldn't be expecting much out of a 13" TV, but still.
<br />
<br />Point is, they're just not made how they used to be.  Probably better off waiting for OLED to drop in price and get something like that.  No ghosting/blur, no burn in, brighter colours, lightweight.

		

