	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Without a rgb mod and a up scanner (xrgb) no HD TV will look good.
<br />Id say any HD TV with interlaced video looks bad the internal scalers are terrible.
<br />With my Samsung dlp and my xrgb2 plus all my Interlaced rgb and component game systems look awesome.
<br />One of the best screens I have for composite video is an old c64 monitor.
<br />Once TVs started to use more digital circuits composite video took a beating.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
